Package: tidyllm
Title: Tidy Large Language Model Integration for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Eduard", "BrÃ¼ll", , "eduard.bruell@zew.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: TidyLLM is an R package designed to seamlessly integrate various large language model APIs, such as Claude, ChatGPT, Groq, and local models via Ollama, into R workflows. It supports text and media-based interactions, interactive message history, stateful handling of rate limits, and tidy pipeline-oriented functionality for easy integration into data workflows.
